nexml.meta: Maculirhamdia stictonota had 277 versus 278 character states in the original publication. I'm not sure which character has a state missing. Alyssa Block (Mabee Lab, 4 June 2009). All characters were hand entered into Mesquite from the original dissertation (versus the matrix that Bockmann sent, which didn't correspond to his dissertation matrix). Alyssa Block 4 June 2009. We will be merging these data into this file. Mastiglanis asopos has a dash that appears to be two smaller dashes combined, thus I split them into characters 268 and 269, but I am not sure this is correct. However, without this split, this taxa would also have only 277 characters versus 278. Alyssa Block 8 June 2009.
